This paper deals with optimization of packet inter-delivery time in cyber-physical systems, which involves the integration of computer systems and physical processes. This falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the use of algorithms and optimization techniques, which are common in the categories of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.MA), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
